The app sets no HTTP security headers. No `X-Content-Type-Options`, `Strict-Transport-Security`, `X-Frame-Options`, etc.

**Recommendation — add `helmet`:**
```js
const helmet = require('helmet');
app.use(helmet());
```

This sets ~15 security headers in one call, including CSP, HSTS, X-Frame-Options, and more.

---

### 🟠 High-Severity Issues

#### 4. No Rate Limiting (OWASP A04:2021 – Insecure Design)

Both endpoints are wide open to abuse — brute force, scraping, or DoS.

**Recommendation:**
